"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-jannik-sinner-withdraws-paris-olympics-novak-djokovic-b1172740.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Men's tennis world No1Jannik Sinnerhas pulled out of theOlympicson the advice of doctors after contracting tonsillitis.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games  Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year  Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions  Reset your wellbeing for the year ahead  The Italian, whocaptured a maiden Grand Slam title at the Australian Openin January,struggled with dizzinessin his Wimbledon quarter-final defeat by Daniil Medvedev earlier this month.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.8560843018401634, \"rank\": 0.16765824155792164, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniil_Medvedev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniil Medvedev\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniil_Medvedev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniil_Medvedev\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had been readying himself for a return to clay with a practice week in Monaco but started feeling ill on Monday evening and has since been told to skip the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"score\": 0.9948705003393791, \"rank\": 0.005153168660795312, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AS_Monaco_FC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The withdrawal of Sinner, who was also scheduled to compete in the doubles with Lorenzo Musetti, means 37-year-old Novak Djokovic will be top seed when the men's singles draw is made on Thursday.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1048, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}, {\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinner wrote on his social media channels: \\\"I am saddened to inform you that unfortunately I will not be able to participate in the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After a good week of clay training, I started to feel unwell.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I spent a couple of days resting and during a visit, the doctor found tonsillitis and strongly advised me against playing.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Missing the Games is a huge disappointment as it was one of my main goals for this season.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not wait to have the honour of representing my country in this very important event.\\\"\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinner would have been a strong contender for at least a podium position at Roland Garros after reaching the French Open semi-finals there last month, losing in five tight sets to eventual champion Carlos Alcaraz.\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1802, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999999809244857, \"rank\": 1.8324181975666515e-08, \"text\": \"French Open\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE 